---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<section id="contacto" class="py-32 bg-[#050505]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 max-w-screen-xl grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <span class="text-sky-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">contáctame</span>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold">Contacto</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl font-light leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
               Estoy buscando mi próxima gran oportunidad para crecer como desarrollador. Si buscas un perfil proactivo y adaptable, hablemos.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-lg text-gray-400 pt-2">
                <Icon name="tabler:map-pin" class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-500" />
                <span>España, Barcelona</span>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3 font-medium">Descarga mi CV:</p>
                <a href="/Nil_Arroyo_CV.pdf" download="Nil_Arroyo_CV.pdf" class="inline-block group relative transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-300">
                    <img 
                        src="/cv-screenshot.jpg" 
                        alt="Descargar CV" 
                        class="w-40 rounded-xl shadow-2xl border-2 border-gray-800 group-hover:border-sky-500 transition-colors"
                    />
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-xl">
                        <Icon name="tabler:download" class="w-10 h-10 text-white" />
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xgolwbzp" 
              method="POST"
              class="space-y-5 bg-[#0f1115] p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-gray-800 shadow-2xl">
        
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2 text-sm">Nombre</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" required class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-base transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2 text-sm">Email</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" required class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-base transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <label class="text-gray-400 font-medium ml-2 text-sm">Mensaje</label>
                <textarea rows="4" name="message" required class="bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-xl focus:border-sky-500 focus:outline-none text-white text-base transition focus:ring-1 focus:ring-sky-500/50"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-white text-black py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition font-bold text-lg mt-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                Enviar Mensaje <Icon name="tabler:send" />
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-gray-600 text-base mt-24 border-t border-gray-900 pt-8">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nil Arroyo. Built with Astro & Tailwind.</p>
    </div>
</section>